          "LAB"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "In life, you were a playwright - though not a very good one. Ironically, though, that’s not why you were Embraced. You were just an unlucky victim of a sire who lost control, felt bad and brought you over to try and make up for draining you. Not the most auspicious start in life, but you were determined to make the best of a bad situation once you’d gotten over the initial shock of becoming a vampire. You gave up on having any artistic inclination a long time ago, and prefer to act as a critic among the rest of your clan. And you are determined to gain power within your clan in spite of your lack of artistic leanings. You were Whip in Tallahassee and then Cincinnati, but found your efforts to move up stymied and curtailed by your Elders. So when San Diego became a Camarilla domain, you saw a golden opportunity. And then San Diego fell. So now you're stuck on the West Coast, Los Angeles is besiged on all sides, and you just found out the Primogen is a neonate not even 50 years kindred.  You’re 120 years old, you’re good enough, and it is your turn. Do whatever you have, crush whomever you must, but you will be Toreador Primogen or die trying."
        ],
